'''''Parma Nölé'' 12''' is the twelfth issue of the [[North East Tolkien Society]] journal ''[[Parma Nölé]]'', for Spring/Summer 2005.

==Contents==
* Melissa S. Gibson: "Language & Literature: The Courtship of Valinor and Iceland"
* Maureen Woodman: "An Opinion Piece"
* Interview with Ancanar's Ralph Lister
* Wendy S. Delmater: "Fëanor"
* Kristyna Lavicka: "Namarië," "Estelio," & "Middle-earth"
